title: Squeaky Gates
description: "Squeaky Gates" is a sound design sample pack featuring a range of wood and metal gate creaks recorded with a shotgun and contact microphone.
longDescription:
"Squeaky Gates" is a sound design sample pack featuring a range of wood and metal gate creaks recorded with a shotgun and contact microphone.


The "Squeaky Gates" sound effects library contains a vast collection of wood and metal gate creak, groan, open & close, spring, mechanism and latch sounds. It provides game developers with a versatile set of resources to enhance their projects. The carefully recorded creaks and groans of gates can add an authentic and realistic touch of gates and latches, the medieval sound of old doors and mechanisms or deep cinematic groans - the range of possibilities is considerable.


With almost 250 individual files, the variety of files is considerable and would be a great addition to a gave developers toolkit with in and out fades to ensure seamless loops and playback.

Features: (Please include a full, comprehensive list of the features of the product)

  • Seamless Looping
